de.cau.cs.kieler.sim.kiem.config.properties
Class KiemConfigEvent

java.lang.Object
  de.cau.cs.kieler.sim.kiem.config.properties.KiemConfigEvent

public class KiemConfigEvent
extends java.lang.Object

Slightly modified version of the original KiemEvent. This class implements some constants that define specific events in KIEM. A DataComponent may register itself using the AbstractDataComponent.provideEventOfInterest method to be a listener of some events. The method AbstractDataComponent.notifyEvent will then be called by KIEM for the registered events.

Author:
Christian Motika - cmot AT informatik.uni-kiel.de
